
This directory contains following scripts:

[1] index-faces-local.py: creates a face-collection for reference images stored in 'ref-faces' directory.

[2] index-faces-s3.py: creates a face-collection for references images in S3 photo-bucket.

[3] recognize-face.py: performs face recognition on a given image-file.

	Usage: python recognize-face.py IMAGE COLLECTION

	where, COLLECTION is created by adding face images using one of the 'index-faces' scripts above.
	
	Script recognize-face.py compares the given IMAGE against the faces indexed in the COLLECTION, and 
	returns the best match.
